quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  42,45,"A tinay …ďe kadi, he…ďe mbee…ďitee e magge, hara he…ďe njankinii koyeera on, he…ďe ndaarira ndaar…óe leppagol. GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen mbi'aya: "Ko woni hayru …ďe …ďeen, ko …ďen hayrim…ďe ko'e mun e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin √Ďalnde Darngal". Nganndee pellet, too√Īu…ďe …ďeen no e lepte duumii…óe."
  42,46,"Yi…ó…ďe alanaa …ďe, ko wallitoo …ďe, hara wonaa Allah. Kala noon mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo."
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado √Īalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa …óuum ka Allah. Nden √Īalnde, faaborde alanaa on, jeddugol kadi alanaa oon."
  42,48,"Si …ďe …óuurnike non, haray min nuliraali ma, aynoowo …ďe: fawaaki ma, si wonaa joottingol. Si wonii Min mee…óiniri ne…ó…óanke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non he…ďi …ďe, sabu kon ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri, a taway pellet, ne…ó…óo on ko jeddu…óo sanne !"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko o muuyi. Homo ye…óa mo o muuyani …ďi…ď…ďe rew…ďe, O ye…óa kadi mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe."
  42,50,"maa O jillira …ďe wor…ďe e rew…ďe; Homo wa…óa dimaro, on mo o muuyani. Pellet, ko O gandu…óo, kattan…óo."
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óaŇčke, nde Allah yeewtata mo, si wonaa wahayu, maa e …ďaawo heedo, maa o immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duŇčayee(sakkitoore) makko, ko ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O toowu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."